mdxmlconverter.temporary

Class TemporaryRelationship

  • java.lang.Object
    • uml.UmlRelationship
      • mdxmlconverter.temporary.TemporaryRelationship

  • public class TemporaryRelationship
extends UmlRelationship
    Auxiliary class extending the UmlRelationship with references to the client element and supplier element since the resolving of all references is only possible after all UmlElements have been converted
    Author:
    dschoenicke
